  "detailed_description": "In China,we call guys who spend excessive money on video games “kelao”.Some early Chinese online games used to induce players to pay to crush non-paying users and monsters in the game. This game aims to restore the Chinese style of online games where players can recharge without spending real money, and let players experience the fun of \"kelao\"!(This is a single player game.)<br>If you are interested in our game, come and add to the wishlist of \"Chinese Online Game\"!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>We are working on the English version and expect it to be available around the time of the official launch,so stay tuned please!Welcome “kelao” to our official discord！</strong></h2><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Super Multiple Endings Multi-Week Program</h2></strong><br>There are about 10+ different endings for different experiences!<br>Do you want to recharge like crazy and become the lord of the Imperial City? Or do you want to develop steadily and get a beautiful woman? It's your choice!<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single-player gameplay simulates the fun of online gaming in a way you've never experienced before!</h2></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/4dd705b54914add9a01a648acecf98be.poster.avif?t=1773392380\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/4dd705b54914add9a01a648acecf98be.webm?t=1773392380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/4dd705b54914add9a01a648acecf98be.mp4?t=1773392380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience Chinese online games with Sims gameplay!</h2></strong><br>The moment you enter the game, you are encouraged to drop everything and go to the online game to show off your skills, in order to one day be the lord of the Imperial City in the online game! However, at the same time when you are having a great time, you also fall into an endless abyss without realizing it...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/d89bb56a712976c530ad0d30b21dd913.poster.avif?t=1773392380\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/d89bb56a712976c530ad0d30b21dd913.webm?t=1773392380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/bd9b84e993e799a503bb9f925a0afbec.poster.avif?t=1773392380\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/bd9b84e993e799a503bb9f925a0afbec.webm?t=1773392380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416920/extras/bd9b84e993e799a503bb9f925a0afbec.mp4?t=1773392380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >pay to Win!</h2></strong></h2></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >in the Game 99.99$ Charge At Will;</h2></h2>Charged to let you experience the thrill of a knife 999;<br>After charging, you can go to the field, go to the imperial city, go to the arena, hanging the white whoring \"players\" who do not charge money;<br>As long as you want, at any time you can rely on kryptonite on the peak of the game, to become a list of big brother, to experience the joy of the first leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinli